text: Hi! Welcome to the terminal demo.
Heh, here's a fun one! But I won't do it unless you ask for it...
Yeah, wreck my eyeballs with blink!
Maybe you need to enable blinking text in your virtual terminal?
What else do we have here?
... that last one was "invisible", if that wasn't visible.
Which one would you like to take?

Before disembarking, please remember to [select value={0} yes="[blink]" no="[b]"/]always[/] use escape sequences [b][reverse][red]r[/red][yellow]e[/yellow][green]s[/green][cyan]p[/cyan][blue]o[/blue][purple]n[/purple][red]s[/red][yellow]i[/yellow][green]b[/green][cyan]l[/cyan][blue]y[/]
